gomodel:SYNGO_1361  a     owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: Fig9 shows quantitative immuno-EM for BRAG1 in mouse hippocampus. The most gold particles are detected directly adjacent (within 30 nm, is about the size of the primary and secondary antibody combined) to the post-synaptic membrane with little particles detected at the presynaptic side.\n\n25/10/2017 Pim\n- IQSEC2; BRAG1; IQ-ArfGEF binds PSD-95 a marker of the PSD.. Experimental description: M&M: \"For post-embedding immunostaining, mice were perfused... \"" ;
